<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>وَالْأَمَانَةِ وَقَدْ ذَكَرَ لَهُ ابْنُ الْجَوْزِيِّ فِي <span class="c2">«الْمُنْتَظَمِ»</span> آثَارًا حَسَنَةً وَأَفْعَالًا جَمِيلَةً <span class="special">﵀</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>